setFormation 
Game: Operation Flashpoint (1.00) 
Description: Set group formation.Formation is one of:  "COLUMN" "STAG COLUMN" "WEDGE 
" "ECH LEFT" "ECH RIGHT" "VEE" "LINE" "FILE" (ArmA) "DIAMOND" (ArmA 
) 
Syntax:  
 group setFormation formation 
Parameters: 
group: Object or Group 
formation: String 
Return Value: 
 Nothing